description: The Akatsuki dispatch an army of powerful reanimated shinobi and White Zetsu across the war zone, causing chaos within the Allied Shinobi Forces' chain of command.

Brilliant Military Advisor of the Hidden Leaf
Military Advisor of the Hidden Leaf

title: The Brilliant Military Advisor of the Hidden Leaf

description: As Darui and his First Company engage an army of White Zetsu, the remaining forces must deal with reanimated shinobi comprised of their late friends—and their worst enemies.
title: Battleground!

description: Darui manages to seal away Ginkaku. Fueled by the rage of losing his brother, Kinkaku transforms into a monster that resembles a Jinchuriki's Tailed Beast State.
title: Golden Bonds

description: Atsui, Samui, and Darui face off against Kinkaku and Ginkaku, the legendary brothers from the Hidden Cloud.
title: Forbidden Words

description: The Ino-Shika-Cho trio is ordered by Shikaku to take down the reanimated Asuma.
title: True Kindness

description: Kankuro's Commando Unit is cornered by Hanzo's poison attack. Fortunately, Mifune and his Fifth Company arrive in time to provide assistance.
title: Mifune vs. Hanzo

description: Choji is unable to attack Asuma and loses his will to fight.
title: The Complete Ino-Shika-Cho Formation!

description: Ino sees Sakura falling from the sky. Although she manages to save her, the shock of the fall has left Sakura with amnesia.
title: Road to Sakura

description: The news of Danzo becoming Hokage and issuing orders to dispose of Sasuke reaches Naruto and Sakura. The two decide to confront Danzo, only to be halted by Kakashi.
title: The Sixth Hokage Danzo

description: Karui and Omoi of the Hidden Cloud press Naruto to give up information regarding Sasuke. Naruto realizes their motives, but decides he cannot sell out his friend.

input: The Eve of the Five Kage Summit
Eve of the Five Kage Summit

title: The Eve of the Five Kage Summit

description: The Five Kage assemble in the Land of Iron to hold the Five Kage Summit Conference.
title: Naruto's Plea

description: Naruto, Yamato, and Kakashi follow Team Samui in the hopes of meeting the Raikage and asking him to spare Sasuke's life.
title: Enter the Five Kage!

description: Madara makes a sudden appearance before Naruto and reveals the truth behind Itachi's actions.
title: Racing Lightning

description: Mifune calls for the formation of the Allied Shinobi Forces to counter the Akatsuki and proposes the Hokage to lead them.
title: A Painful Decision

description: In the Land of Iron, Sasuke and the Raikage fight a battle to the death when Gaara, the Kazekage, intervenes.
title: Sasuke's Ninja Way

description: By resurrecting the monster Ten Tails and becoming its Jinchuriki Host, Madara plots to bring the entire world under his Genjutsu control.
title: Declaration of War

description: Having blocked the combined attacks of Gaara, Temari, Kankuro, and Darui with his Susano'o, Sasuke goes after Danzo.
title: Power of the Five Kage

description: Killer Bee engages in a deadly battle against Kisame, who has come to capture the Eight-Tails.

input: The Tailed Beast vs. The Tailless Tailed Beast
Tailed Beast vs. The Tailless Tailed Beast
Beast vs. The Tailless Tailed Beast

title: The Tailed Beast vs. The Tailless Tailed Beast

description: Sakura arrives in the Land of Iron to speak with Naruto, but her confession surprises him. Elsewhere, Kisame appears before Killer Bee.
title: Sakura's Feelings

description: Naruto learns from Sai that Sakura intends to kill Sasuke. The Sand arrive to brief the Leaf Ninja about what happened at the Five Kage Summit.
title: As One's Friend

description: As Sakura heads toward Sasuke, she begins to recollect fond memories of Team 7.
title: Sakura's Resolve

description: Kakashi decides to go after Sakura to stop her, while Yamato and Naruto are ordered to return to the Leaf Village.
title: Danzo's Right Arm

description: Danzo's uncanny jutsu prevents Sasuke from landing a clean hit on his enemy. As Karin attempts to analyze Danzo's jutsu, Madara recognizes it as Izanagi, the Uchiha's Forbidden Visual Jutsu.
title: The Forbidden Visual Jutsu

description: Danzo believes he's won the battle against Sasuke. Little does he realize, Sasuke placed him under genjutsu before they last exchanged blows.
title: Danzo Shimura

description: Sakura tells Sasuke that she wants to desert the village and join him. A skeptical Sasuke tells Sakura he will believe her if she can finish off Karin.
title: The Burden

description: Sasuke reveals that he killed Danzo and goes on to declare his intent to purify the Uchiha clan's name by annihilating the Hidden Leaf.
title: Two Fates

description: Realizing what it means to gain something precious and then lose it, Naruto sneaks out of the inn to follow Sakura and Kakashi to find Sasuke.
title: Lost Bonds

description: The formation of the Allied Shinobi Forces is ratified by the Feudal Lords of the Five Great Nations. Each Kage returns to their village to prepare for the coming war.
title: The Five Great Nations Mobilize

description: Having become a high-level shinobi, Naruto is now able to understand Sasuke's heart, and he tells Sasuke to direct all of his hatred towards him.
title: High-Level Shinobi

description: Bee believes Samehada has taken a liking to him but is unaware that this is all just part of the Akatsuki's plan.
title: Infiltrator

description: Naruto gathers his friends and tells them that he will defeat Sasuke alone. Meanwhile, the Elders of the Leaf officially nominate Kakashi to become the next Hokage.
title: Kakashi Hatake, the Hokage

description: At Mount Myoboku, Naruto prepares to store Gerotora within himself, but hesitates as it also holds the potential risk of unleashing the Nine Tails.
title: Storage

description: The Five Kage assemble in the Hidden Cloud Village to discuss where to hide the remaining two Jinchuriki.
title: The Five Kage's Decision

description: In Mount Myoboku, Gerotora, Fukasaku, and the Great Lord Elder are debating whether to give Naruto the key to the Tetragram Seal left behind by Jiraiya, an act that could unleash the Nine Tails.

input: Prophecy of the Great Lord Elder

title: Prophecy of the Great Lord Elder

description: Tsunade sends out Naruto under the guise of a top-secret mission to keep him hidden away from the Akatsuki.

input: The Young Man and the Sea

title: The Young Man and the Sea

description: During their voyage, Naruto, Yamato, Gai, and Aoba stop at an island to recover from severe seasickness. There, they unexpectedly meet up with Sakura, Ino, and Choji.
title: The Ninja of Benisu

description: Naruto's ship is stranded at sea, when another ship suddenly appears. Believing it to be a ghost ship, Naruto panics until he finds Hishaku, a sailor, on board.
title: The Cursed Ghost Ship

description: Pirates living on an island resembling a battleship open fire on Naruto's ship. Using Yamato's Wood Style Jutsu, Naruto and the others escape into an undersea cave.
title: Battleship Island

description: Naruto, Yamato, and Aoba arrive on an island where they spot a young woman. While trying to gather information, Aoba learns of a horrible secret hidden on the island.
title: The Forgotten Island

description: Naruto and the other crew members find their ship infested with poisonous mushrooms. To make matters worse, the mushrooms have destroyed all of their food and supplies, making their voyage into one of survival.

input: Eat or Die! Mushrooms from Hell

title: Eat or Die! Mushrooms from Hell

description: Naruto's Shadow Clones turn against him after feeling mistreated and overworked. Unable to undo his jutsu, Naruto is taken captive.
title: Revenge of the Shadow Clones

description: As he prepares for the coming war, Shikamaru begins to feel the pressure of having to shoulder the lives of his friends.
title: The Closed Route

description: Guy recalls the celebration after Lee learned the Hidden Lotus technique.
title: Fight! Rock Lee!

description: Hinata's father Hiashi summons the Hyuga clan to discuss the role they will be playing in the upcoming Fourth Great Ninja War.
title: The Girls Get-Together

description: Naruto and the others encounter a thief who claims that he is Naruto Uzumaki of the Hidden Leaf.
title: Naruto's Imposter

description: Naruto meets two kunoichi named Shizuka and Tokiwa from the Nadeshiko village who are looking for Jiraiya's student.
title: The Kunoichi of Nadeshiko Village

description: At the Ninja Academy, Shino recounts the time when he failed to capture a wanted thief.
title: Friends You Can Count On

description: Sai meets some kids who remind him of Sakura and Naruto. Sai is amused when he is asked what the difference between a comrade and a friend is—an answer he himself is not sure of.
title: Sai's Day Off

description: Ino, Choji, and Shikamaru run into Kosuke, an elderly genin who they saved in a previous mission.
title: The Legendary Ino-Shika-Cho Trio

description: Feeling desperate, Kiba asks Kakashi to train him. Although busy with his own mission, Kakashi respects Kiba's wish and summons his Ninja Hounds as a training partner.
title: Kiba's Determination

description: As the Leaf Ninja's ship heads toward their final stop, Yamato warns the crew to stay alert for enemies who could mimic both the appearance and chakra of their closest allies.
title: Kakashi, My Eternal Rival!

description: Naruto runs into Akatsuchi and Kurotsuchi of the Hidden Stone, who are on an assignment to deliver a letter from the Tsuchikage addressed to the Mizukage.
title: Naruto's Vow

description: Hearing that Killer Bee has complete control over Eight Tails, Naruto asks for training to control his own Nine Tails' power, but is quickly rejected.

input: Land Ahoy! Is This the Island of Paradise?
Ahoy! Is This the Island of Paradise?
Is This the Island of Paradise?

title: Land Ahoy! Is This the Island of Paradise?

description: Motoi warns Naruto that he is not yet ready to undergo training to control the Tailed Beast. Undaunted, Naruto asks Motoi to tell him more about Killer Bee.
title: Killer Bee and Motoi

description: Naruto continues his battle against Nine Tails to take control of its immense power. But exposure to Nine Tails' hatred begins to take its toll on Naruto.
title: The Orange Spark

description: With Killer Bee as his new master, Naruto begins his training to control the power of a Tailed Beast. In order to do so, one must fight the Tailed Beast head on and absorb its chakra.

input: The Next Challenge! Naruto vs. Nine Tails!!
Next Challenge! Naruto vs. Nine Tails!!

title: The Next Challenge! Naruto vs. Nine Tails!!

description: Unbeknownst to everyone in the Hidden Leaf Village, a dangerous enemy plots to free the Nine Tails from Kushina, the Jinchuriki Host.
title: Target: Nine Tails

description: Minato is forced to use his Flying Raijin Jutsu and leave his wife Kushina's side to save their newborn son Naruto from a masked assailant.
title: The Fourth Hokage's Death Match

description: Minato uses his Transportation Technique to move the Nine Tails away from the Hidden Leaf Village.
title: Thank You

description: Guy tries to prevent Kisame from delivering intel to the Akatsuki, and a battle ensues between the two.

input: Battle in Paradise! The Odd Beast vs. The Monster!
in Paradise! The Odd Beast vs. The Monster!
Paradise! The Odd Beast vs. The Monster!
The Odd Beast vs. The Monster!

title: Battle in Paradise! The Odd Beast vs. The Monster!

description: Aoba enters Kisame's mind to gather intel on the Akatsuki. In the process he learns about the ex-Hidden Mist ninja's bloody past.
title: The Man Named Kisame

description: Madara appears in the Hidden Rain Village seeking the corpse of Nagato and his Rinnegan.
title: The Angelic Herald of Death

description: Kabuto and a reanimated Deidara attempt to grab hold of the Jinchuriki, but are stopped by the Tsuchikage.
title: The Artist Returns

description: Aoba assigns Naruto an S-rank mission to distract him from learning about their true mission: keeping the two Jinchuriki hidden from the enemy.
title: The Super Secret S-Rank Mission!

description: A look back into the early years when Naruto and Sasuke first met and got to know each other.
title: Meeting

description: The Allied Shinobi Forces and the Akatsuki complete their final preparations for battle. The Fourth Great Ninja War is about to begin!
title: Assemble! Allied Shinobi Forces!

description: During the Chunin Exam, Sasuke witnesses Naruto's growth as a shinobi and comes to acknowledge his teammate as a rival.
title: Rivals

description: Sasuke's defeat to Gaara, and later Itachi, forces him to realize that he is not strong enough to get revenge against his older brother.
title: Rift

description: Naruto is determined to save Sasuke, who has deserted the Hidden Leaf to join Orochimaru.
title: Parting

description: Kankuro's commando unit is immediately ambushed by the Akatsuki's own unit comprised of the reanimated Deidara and Sasori.
title: War Begins

description: The Allied Shinobi Forces are on standby, ready to confront Madara's army of reanimated shinobi and 100,000 White Zetsu.
title: For My Friend

description: Under the guidance of Killer Bee, Naruto enters the final stage of training to master the Tailed Beast Bomb, a Jinchuriki's most powerful technique.
title: Secrets of the Reanimation Jutsu

description: Kabuto uses the Reanimation Jutsu to summon the most powerful members of the Seven Ninja Swordsmen of the Mist.
title: The First and Last Opponent

description: The commando unit is in hot water as they engage the reanimated Kekkei Genkai shinobi, which include Zabuza Momochi and Haku.
title: An Old Nemesis Returns
